OL,5, Mortgage deals have been withdrawn by  
OL,6, some banks and building societies after
OL,7, a fall in the pound fuelled forecasts  
OL,8, of a sharp rise in interest rates.     
OL,10,FYorkshire Building Society joined      
OL,11,FVirgin Money and Skipton Building      
OL,12,FSociety in halting mortgage offers for 
OL,13,Fnew customers.                         
OL,15,FHalifax said it would stop mortgages   
OL,16,Fwith product fees.                     
OL,18,FThe Bank of England said on Monday it  
OL,19,Fwould "not hesitate" to hike interest  
OL,20,Frates after the pound hit record lows. 
